# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================

# 1. Never commit this file with real private keys or API keys
# 2. Use different keys for different environments (testnet vs mainnet)
# 3. Regularly rotate your private keys and API keys
# 4. Use hardware wallets for production deployments
# 5. Set up proper monitoring and alerting for production systems
